com.sun.media.jsdt.http

Class TCPSocketFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.media.jsdt.impl.JSDTObject
      • com.sun.media.jsdt.http.TCPSocketFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSDTDebugFlags, JSDTSocketFactory, java.io.Serializable

    public class TCPSocketFactory
extends JSDTObject
implements JSDTSocketFactory
    TCPSocketFactory creates a direct socket connection to the specified port on the specified host. Based on the sun.rmi.transport.proxy.RMIDirectSocketFactory class.
